"The punishments, blabla..."

50:17.658 --> 50:20.537
I say it means

50:20.538 --> 50:24.412
That the government does
not want to arrest him.

50:25.575 --> 50:29.699
If they do, they get an
international problem.

50:29.700 --> 50:32.032
- Ma'am, enough.
- Because it's political.

50:32.033 --> 50:37.933
Government is concerned to
pursue it, but not to arrest it.

50:37.934 --> 50:39.557
Never.

50:39.558 --> 50:42.140
The senator is a communist,
like you and me.

50:42.141 --> 50:44.782
Yes, but it has
special protection.

50:44.783 --> 50:46.990
And I'll toast to that,

50:46.991 --> 50:50.740
Because we all need
the senator poet

50:50.741 --> 50:54.075
Keep writing about the
suffering of the people.

50:57.475 --> 51:00.074
Madam, he is protected by the
leadership of the Party.

51:00.075 --> 51:02.990
Do you know what I want to know?
Listen...

51:02.991 --> 51:08.349
When communism comes, everyone
will be the same as him.

51:08.350 --> 51:10.408
Or will they be the same as me?

51:11.491 --> 51:15.657
To me, I've been cleaning
up the fucking bourgeois.

51:15.658 --> 51:18.458
Since I'm 11 years old.

51:25.350 --> 51:27.300
They will all be the same to me.

51:28.558 --> 51:32.200
Let's eat in bed and
fornicate in the kitchen.

51:34.575 --> 51:37.475
For that we fight, comrade!

51:43.075 --> 51:45.824
"In Bogot they met
Morinigo, Trujillo,"

51:45.825 --> 51:49.533
Gonzales Videla, Somoza,
